information = The Veridian Pyrohydra is a mythical beast believed to be a manifestation of the forest's wrath. Legends say it appears when ancient woodlands are threatened by destruction or desecration. This enormous hydra-like creature has scales that shimmer with an emerald hue, and it can breathe devastating green flames from its many heads.
notes = The origins of the Veridian Pyrohydra are shrouded in mystery, with some saying it was created by an ancient druidic ritual to protect sacred groves. It is said to appear during times of great environmental peril, attacking those who pose a threat to the natural order. Its green flames are both a symbol of the forest's fury and a means to cleanse the land of invaders.

